line: Oh, well, uh, she knows. I mean, we don't really buy into that kind of crap, to the extent that love is an expression of familiarity over time, my access to infinite timelines precludes the necessity of attachment. In fact, I even abandoned one of my infinite daughters in an alternate version of earth that was taken over by mutants.

name: Pickle Rick
line: Huh? Uh, no. No, nope, sorry about that. Nope, just me. Yeesh!

name: Pickle Rick

name: Dr. Wong
line: I've heard a lot about you today. Your family is crazy about you. Your daughter holds you in very high regard. You're a lucky fella.

name: Pickle Rick

line: Dad I would like you to tell me what's in the syringe.

name: Pickle Rick
line: It's a serum that I need to, uh, to stay alive. I have had a rough day. And, uh, I've sustained a lot of damage. I'm pretty close to death, which the serum will prevent.

name: Dr. Wong
line: By changing you from a pickle to a human.

name: Pickle Rick

name: Dr. Wong

name: Pickle Rick

name: Dr. Wong
line: Why didn't you want to come here?

name: Pickle Rick
line: Because I don't respect therapy, because I'm a scientist. Because I invent, transform, create, and destroy for a living, and when I don't like something about the world, I change it. And I don't think going to a rented office in a strip mall to listen to some agent of averageness explain which words mean which feelings has ever helped anyone do anything.  I think it's helped a lot of people get comfortable and stop panicking, which is a state of mind we value in the animals we eat, but not something I want for myself. I'm not a cow. I'm a pickle. When I feel like it. So...you asked.

name: Dr. Wong
line: Rick, the only connection between your unquestionable intelligence and the sickness destroying your family is that everyone in your family, you included, use intelligence to justify sickness.  You seem to alternate between viewing your own mind as an unstoppable force and as an inescapable curse. And I think it's because the only truly unapproachable concept for you is that it's your mind within your control. You chose to come here, you chose to talk -to belittle my vocation- just as you chose to become a pickle.  You are the master of your universe, and yet you are dripping with rat blood and feces. Your enormous mind literally vegetating by your own hand.  I have no doubt that you would be bored senseless by therapy, the same way I'm bored when I brush my teeth and wipe my ass. Because the thing about repairing, maintaining, and cleaning is it's not an adventure. There's no way to do it so wrong you might die. It's just work. And the bottom line is, some people are okay going to work, and some pee well, some people would rather die. Each of us gets to choose.

name: Pickle Rick
line: I, um I'm sorry I lied to get out of the thing. I, I shouldn't lie to you.

name: Morty
line: Th-th-that sounds really violent.

name: Rick
line: It’s not a literal bone, Morty.

name: Morty
line: Oh, Okay.

name: Employee Morty
line: Brace yourself, the process does also break every bone in your body.

name: Morty
line: Wait, ahhhh! Ooh, ow!

line: I like crayons.

name: Toddler Morty 2
line: Girls are gross.

name: Morty
line: I-I-I think I feel like myself again.

name: Rick
line: Eh, you look a little weird. Your skin’s all pink like a baby mouse. Is that normal?

name: Employee Morty
line: Probably. Uh, sign here for storage or disposal of the twenty-six years we removed.

name: Rick
line: Wait, what? I ain’t payin’ to store twenty-six years.

name: Employee Morty
line: Well, then you’re taking it with you.

name: Twenty-Six Year Old Morty
line: I’m almost ready to sell out.

name: Rick
line: Alright, what’s disposal cost?

name: Twenty-Six Year Old Morty
line: S-something unfair’s happening!

name: Deformed Morty
line: There’s no escape! No escape!

name: Twenty-Six Year Old Morty
line: Let me help you, this is not a good look!

name: Rick
line: Oh boy.

name: Morty
line: Hey, they shot me!

name: Police Morty
line: You are seriously hurting the Citadel experience!

name: Deformed Morty
line: Listen to me!

name: Police Morty
line: Drop the gun!

name: Deformed Morty
line: Death is coming for us all, and the Citadel is a weapon of mass destruc—

name: Rick
line: Woof. You’re about to get suspended with pay. Come on, Morty. Let’s get out of here before this gets political.

name: Twenty-Six Year Old Morty
line: U-uh. Was I influential?

name: Morty
line: Yeah, y-you were influential. You had like seven— seven blogs.

name: Twenty-Six Year Old Morty
line: Tight. Uh.

name: Rick
line: Ugh. Too late.

name: Secret Service Rick
line: C-137. President Morty requests you join him for dinner.

name: Morty
line: Woah! S-seriously?

name: Rick
line: You know I destroyed this place?

name: Secret Service Rick
line: You’ve been pardoned for that, sir.

name: Morty
line: Rick, let’s have dinner with the Morty president.

name: Rick
line: Morty, the idea was to get back to simple adventures. The Citadel runs on canon.

name: Morty
line: Okay. I guess things really are going right back to how they were.

name: Rick
line: Fine, I could eat. But the second he reveals he’s evil, we’re gone.

name: Morty
line: I don’t know. Tastes pretty good.

name: Rick
line: Okay, let me know if you start feeling poisony. Good to have you back, buddy.

name: President Morty
line: Sorry I’m late. Never really ends around here.

name: Rick
line: Look at this Morty. They really did make a you the president.

name: President Morty
line: And I hate ‘em every day for it. But wow, Rick C-137. Now that’s a guy to move your schedule around for. Not-not here to blow the place up again, I hope. Ha ha.

name: Rick
line: Ha. Not unless you try to keep me here.

name: President Morty
line: Geez, wouldn’t dream of it. But it’s amazing you dropped by because I was eventually gonna hunt you down.

name: Rick
line: There’s the reveal. Let’s dance.

name: President Morty
line: Ha, geez.

name: Morty
line: Come on, man. The guy got elected president. By Ricks and Mortys. He’s being really nice.

name: Rick
line: All politicians are nice.

name: President Morty
line: He’s a hot bag of peanuts, isn’t he?

name: Morty
line: We’ve been through a lot, a-and he does not like—

name: Rick
line: Serialized drama.

name: President Morty
line: Right, no drama. Keep it episodic. Ricks never look back. Waste of a legend in his case. You know, he practically built this place.

name: Morty
line: Wait, what?

name: Rick
line: And now you're running it squeaky clean, right? That’s why you got deformed Mortys comin’ up through the sewer lines talking about ‘hope’ and ‘change’.

name: President Morty
line: Fair enough.

name: Morty
line: Good clap-back, Rick. What’s the deal with that, Mr. P?

name: President Morty
line: I got a little project going on, acquired some hands-on labor. It would require less if you were willing to tell me how one might bring down the Central Finite Curve.

name: Rick
line: Alright, time to go Morty.

name: Morty
line: I wanna know what he’s talking about.

name: President Morty
line: Yeah, you’ve come all this way. Can you give me ten more seconds?

name: Rick
line: Literally ten? Because now it would be six.

name: President Morty
line: Oh, I’m fine with that. Make it two… one. Like I said, would’ve been a big help for you to tell me, but I should have everything I need from you now. Let me just make sure…

name: Rick
line: You can’t scan an entire brain over appetizers.

name: President Morty
line: Oh, most of yours got scanned a looong time ago.

name: President Morty
line: You probably don’t remember.

name: Rick Stan Lee
line: Check out season one, episode nine, Rickheads. Excel-uurp-cior!

name: Rick
line: Evil Rick.

name: Morty
line: We kicked his ass.

name: President Morty
line: Evil Rick. I love it. Smartest man in the universe, with an ego so big you could just grab it like a joystick.

name: President Morty
line: Looks complete. I was afraid I’d have to kill every Rick on the Citadel to get what I needed.

name: Morty
line: You asshole! I vouched for you! He only came here because I asked him to. I’m sorry, Rick.

name: Rick
line: That apology and a screwdriver in my hand would be worth one screwdriver.

name: President Morty
line: Pfft, you sell-out Mortys kill me. I’d hate you more than the Ricks you worship if there was any point. But you can’t help it; you were bred for it. Wanna see?

name: President Morty
line: You already know rogue Ricks used Mortys to hide themselves from the Citadel. But you might not know it worked so well that the Citadel became its own Morty market. And I’m sure you don’t know how far they’ve gone to help supply meet demand. Sure, Ricks could scour infinity for naturally-occurring grandsons, but why bother? So much work. Such an admission of need. There are infinite versions of our grandfather, Morty. He’s an infinite smear of one shitty old man, and he’s attached to us infinitely through his weakness and our forgiveness. This is why we’re with him. This is why we’re alive.

name: Morty
line: What the fuck?! Rick, say this isn’t true!

name: Rick
line: It isn’t the whole truth.

name: Morty
line: Liar!

name: President Morty
line: Liar.

name: Rick
line: It’s complicated!

name: Morty
line: I’m not busy!

name: Rick
line: Okay, Morty, remember when all I said I needed was your apology and a screwdriver in my hand? Well, I forgot I literally have a screwdriver in my hand. I mean, duh-doi, I’m basically Inspector Gadget.

name: President Morty
line: Uh oh.

name: President Morty
line: It’s okay, he’s free to go. He’s the Rickest Rick. We’ll never see him again.

name: Rick
line: Morty, when you came here for that serum did you refill this gun?

name: Morty
line: Yeah.

name: Morty
line: Holy shit!

name: Rick
line: I only know one man that ever hacked my Portal Gun, and it turned out it was evil you.

name: President Morty
line: Yay. He’s all caught up.

name: Rick
line: Wait! Hold it, hold it!

name: Morty
line: Wh-who’s that?

name: Rick
line: Time for Big Boy. Duck!

name: Morty
line: Does he like it?

name: Rick
line: He’s a metaphor for capitalism, Morty. What do you think?

name: Rick
line: Yoink!

name: President Morty
line: You can’t outrun your past, Rick.

name: President Morty
line: Tch, did you think my forcefield would be down the second time?

name: Rick
line: I was expressing disapproval of your dialogue!

name: President Morty
line: Ahaha. Disapprove all you want. Tonight, the quality of dialogue stops mattering. Tonight, I do that thing I wanna do, with the Curve thing.

name: Loudspeaker system
line: Nobody leave, everybody stay. Nobody leave, everybody stay. Nobody leave, everybody stay.

name: Rick D716
line: In uncertain times like these, I think it’s important for me to say: Eat shit, fuck you! The drug companies paid for me to say every word, I have millions of dollars, and I don’t care— oh god oh fuck no, oh—

name: 'Rick D716-B
line: And I’d just like to say that prescription drugs are great and you should buy them now.

name: Morty
line: What’s happening, Rick?

name: Rick
line: He hacked the entire city’s portal supply. Come on, there still might be one way out of here. Out the bottom.

name: Morty
line: What do you think he needed from your brain?

name: Rick
line: I assume schematics for the Citadel’s Dimensional Drive. If he’s gonna use it to blow the Curve, we do not wanna be here.

name: Morty
line: What is the Central Finite Curve?

name: Rick
line: Q and A after our survival. Hopefully we can snag some untainted fluid at the source and get the fuck outta here.

name: Rick
line: Or not.

name: Rick
line: Wow. I thought my capitalism metaphor was on the nose.

name: Morty
line: So did you help build the Citadel? Did you just lie to me about everything?

name: Rick
line: Can’t you just sneak through the cave base? We turned a new leaf, Morty. We’re back to simple adventures.

name: Morty
line: It’s not a new leaf until you tell me everything.

name: Rick
line: Morty, we really don’t have time for this. The whole place is gonna blow.

name: Morty
line: No, I-I don’t trust you. I-I-I don’t wanna do this anymore if I’m not gonna get straight answers from you.

name: Morty
line: Woah. Dead wife?

name: Rick
line: Yes. Now everyone can shut up about it.

name: Morty
line: Wow, Rick. I feel a lot better having seen all that.

name: President Morty
line: Of course that’s the case. In their minds, they’re the underdog.

name: President Morty
line: And that’s how they justify this.

name: Rick
line: Morty, I’m not responsible for every fucked up Rick out there.

name: President Morty
line: They literally all say that. They all have that excuse; it’s part of their system. None of them have to be responsible, they're all victims of themselves. ‘Oh, it’s so hard to be a genius. Couldn’t you just die?’

name: Morty
line: Well what are you doin’ about it?

name: President Morty
line: Jack shit. I’m leaving. Do you know what the Central Finite Curve is? They built a wall around infinity, separated all the infinite universes from all the infinite universes where he’s the smartest man in the universe. Every version of us has spent every version of all of our lives in one infinite crib, built around an infinite fucking baby.

name: President Morty
line: And I’m leaving it. That’s what makes me ‘evil’, being sick of him. If you’ve ever been sick of him, you’ve been evil too.

name: Morty
line: Rick, did you really leave the crows for me? Or did you come back because they dumped you?

name: President Morty
line: There you go, kid. Now you’re Evil Morty too. Sooner or later, we all are, on this side of the Curve.

name: Orange Afro Rick
line: Don’t worry, Morty. We still got a way out they never thought of. Operation Phoenix.

name: Orange Afro Morty
line: Doesn’t that still mean, like, death?

name: Orange Afro Rick
line: Sure, but the joke’s on them cuz we just found a backdoor to getting off this rock.

name: Female computer voice
line: Rerouted. Rerouted. Rerouted.

name: Female computer voice
line: Rerouted. Rerouted. Rerouted.

name: Morty
line: Oh my fucking god!

name: Rick
line: Come on Morty, we gotta go!

name: Morty
line: Woah!

name: President Morty
line: You can come if you want.

name: President Morty
line: Don’t blame me if you don’t.

name: Rick
line: Ugh. From where I sit, Morty, that’s the best deal on the table. I-I don’t have a real plan.

name: Rick
line: Thanks, pal. I-I’m glad you ignored my advice.

name: President Morty
line: It’s just as well. I lied. That second seat’s a toilet.

name: Morty
line: Oh, super dick move. But weirdly kind of cool to admit it.

name: Rick
line: Geez, you guys really are bred for forgiveness. Let’s go.

name: Rick
line: Say goodbye to the Citadel, fellas.

name: Mr. Poopybutthole
line: Woo-wee. Evil Morty. That was quite a scheme. Makes me wonder if there’s an evil me out there. But I guess, sometimes I look at my life, and I may not even need ‘im. Cuz, well, guess I made a pretty big mess of things myself. Ooo eee.

name: Mr. Poopybutthole
line: I never got my job at the university back. Remember that? Rick made me do karate. It was kinda funny, but I guess things went downhill from there.

name: Mr. Poopybutthole
line: Started isolating myself from Amy. Used to tell her everything I was feeling.

name: Mr. Poopybutthole
line: But then I guess I stopped.

name: Mr. Poopybutthole
line: Cuz I wanted her to love who she thought I was, not who I felt myself becoming.

name: Mr. Poopybutthole
line: Ever think about how horrified the people we love would be if they found out who we truly are? So we just dig ourselves deeper, into our lies every day , ultimately only hurting the people who were brave enough to love us.

name: Mr. Poopybutthole
line: Wish I didn’t do that.

name: Mr. Poopybutthole
line: Wish I was brave enough to love them back. I don’t know, maybe you should try it.

name: Mr. Poopybutthole
line: We don’t have as much time as we think. Ooo eee.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: So listen, the heat’s on and  there’s nowhere left to turn so Morty and I are just going to fly my spaceship into a black hole.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: What?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Is that cool with you, dog?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: Rick, no! Mortyyyy!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 4
line: I got it! The call’s coming from… inside the house!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: All Ricks

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: The Ricks are probably gonna waste some time messing with Jerry. They won’t be able to help themselves. But as soon as they get bored they’ll be on to us.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Chair waiter
line: Phones á la clams, and phonesgetti with phoneballs. Anything else?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Yeah, more phonesticks please.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Phone waiter
line: Right away, sir.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: You know Rick, when I first saw all those Ricks and Mortys, I thought ‘gee, that kinda devalues our bond.’ But then I realised that just means that our relationship must be pretty special to span over all those different timelines.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Yeah, it’s gotta be that way. You’re a camouflage.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Camouflage? Wh-wh-what are you talking about, Rick?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Ricks have a very distinct and traceable brainwave due to our genius. The best way to hide from an enemy’s radar is to stand near someone with complementary brainwaves that make ours invisible. See, wh-wh-when a Rick is with a Morty, the genius waves get cancelled out by the uh,  Morty waves.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Um… because… our personalities are so different?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Oh, shit dog! My portal gun was hacked remotely Morty, obviously by the real killer to frame me. But I was able to trace the signal. Come on, let’s go!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Uh-oh!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: ‘Scuse me, we’ve tracked a pair of dangerous criminals to this exact location. They look exactly like us, so in order to avoid confusion I’m going to mark us each with a red X right now. That way if someone has a gun and we both tell you to shoot the other one because they’re the evil one, you’ll know who’s lying.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 2
line: Hey, check it out!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: Dammit!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Chair waiter
line: Hey, you didn’t pay your bill!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: The red X! Red X!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Hey, it’s a good thing that space outlet had labcoats and your favourite kind of shirt in stock, huh Morty?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Yeah, Rick. I-I heard you the first time. You don’t have to keep saying it over and over and over.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Man, this place is wayyy off the grid. This guy does not wanna be found.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Well, if he’s a Rick, doesn’t he just have to stand by a Morty to hide? I mean, isn’t that what Mortys are? Human cloaking devices?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Morty, you’re making a bigger deal out of this than it is.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Oh my god, Rick, look! There’s a bunch of people strapped all over that building!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Not people, Morty. Mortys.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Oh my god… wh-why would somebody do this? It’s horrible!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Well, one Morty’s enough to hide from the bureaucrats. But you g- you get a whole matrix of Mortys and put ‘em in agonising pain. That creates a pattern that can hide even from other Ricks, motherfucker. I fiddled with a  concept like this once.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: On paper, Morty, on paper! I wouldn’t do this, it’s barbaric overkill. I mean, you could accomplish the same result with like five Mortys and a jumper cable.  Which I also wouldn’t do! I’m just saying, it’s bad craftsmanship.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Beth
line: Coffee time!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: Ugh.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Hi Jerry!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: Leave me alone, I’m working!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Oh, you are? Wh-wh-what do you do?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: Ugh. I’m- I’m in between advertising jobs.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Advertising? Wow! So, people need help figuring out what to buy and then y-you help them?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: W-well, it’s a little more complicated than that…

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Well, I mean, you do it, and you seem like a guy that really has it all together!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: Dude, are you… wh- you’re being a dick, right?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Oh gosh, wh- I hope not! I-I-I-I wouldn’t want to offend you in any way!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: You’re really a Rick?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Ohoho! Y-of course I am! Just as much as my Morty’s a Morty!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: Hey, he looks a lot like Eric Stoltz from the movie ‘Mask.’ You know, the one with Cher in it?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: That’s right, Jerry! He-he’s from a reality where everyone is Eric Stoltz mask people! He’s Eric Stoltz mask Morty! They assigned him to me because… I never had any kids of my own. But if I did, boy, I’d love ‘em  if they were as smart and as successful as you are, Jerry.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: Hey, get a load of this! Jerry’s hanging out with doofus Rick.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 2
line: Haha, this is perfect.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: I’m not doofus Rick! I’m Rick J-19-Zeta-7!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: Oh, is that the timeline where everybody eats poop? Jerry, you know this guy eats poop, right?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Hey! I don’t eat poop! Y-you guys are always so mean to me!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: I guess it’s only fair to tell you now, Jerry… I’m the worst Rick of them all.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: According to who? Other versions of you? If I’ve learned one thing, it’s that before you get anywhere in life, you gotta stop listening to yourself.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Wow, you really are wise, Jerry. I-I guess that’s why you work in advertising!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: The fact that you feel that way makes you the best Rick of them all.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: You don’t care about me at all! I’m no different than that jacket you’ve got on! Y-y-or-or your stupid portal gun! I’m just a tool! I-I’m just an object!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Hey, it’s your choice to take it personally, Morty. Now for the love of god, be quiet! The point of this is to get the drop on the guy!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: You know what Rick, I’ll tell you something! I’m more than a human shield!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Yeah, that’s right! You are! You’re a perfect impenetrable sheet of human armour, Morty! Because you’re as dumb as I am smart! Which is why when I say ‘shut up’ it’s really good advice.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Great, nice work, Morty.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Urrgh.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: Ooh, look at you, C-137! You’re- aren’t you a tough customer?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: The slow clap? Really? Kinda played out, dude.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: Not in this dimension it isn’t. In fact, hah, I invented it and nobody else has ever even done it here before.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Well lah-dee-dah.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: Hey, that’s mine!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: I don’t like the look of that Rick, Morty. We gotta escape.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: I’m not gonna help you, Rick. Y-you’re a monster.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Don’t be Rickdiculous, Morty.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: W-will you stop saying that? It’s stupid.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: Take his Morty away.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Morty
line: Come with me.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Yeah, gladly. Geez man, Ricks huh?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Hey man, you seem to know how this place works. Is there any way we can… shut down that grid and rescue all those Mortys out there?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Morty
line: It would be pointless. Mortys have no chance of defeating a Rick.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Morty
line: In here.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: Ahh, isn’t it beautiful?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Yeah, yeah, looks like payday at Neverland ranch in here. Zing!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Lobster alien
line: Hehehehehehehehehe.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: That guy got it.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: Ah-ah Rick, quiet. You’re missing my symphony.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Hey, I’ll take it over Mumford and Sons. Zip!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Lobster alien
line: Hehehehehehehehehe.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: This guy is on it!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: He’s not laughing at your dumb jokes, Rick. That’s just a random noise it makes every ten seconds.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Lobster alien
line: Hehehehehehehehehe.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Awww.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: See, Rick, you’re not as clever as you think you are. I wanted you to find me. We’re not so  different, you and I.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Yeah, duh!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: See this right here, Rick? I crunched the numbers, I created a spectrum of all the Ricks. I listed ‘em out from most evil to least evil. Here’s where I am. And look at right here’s where you are, Rick. This guy right here? Super weird.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: I get it. So you want me to team up with you to take down the council of Ricks, right? Is that where you’re going with this? ‘Cause that’s where I’d be going.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: Please. I think I’m doing pretty good on my own. I’m simply going to download the contents of your brain, and then kill you.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Okay, if we add a little more titanium nitrate, and just a tad of chlorified tartrate: ovenless brownies!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: It’s incredible what a gifted mind can accomplish when priorities are in order!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Well, come on, I can’t take all the credit, Jerry. It was your idea. C’mere Jerry!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: Hey, uh. C’mere, uh. I-I wanna show you something.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: Okay, look. Everybody makes fun of me for getting these, but… you’re a genius scientist, what do you think? There’s little R2D2s where the George Washingtons should be!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: You know Jerry, I’m not gonna tell you that these will increase in value, or even hold their current value. The truth is… you bought ‘em ‘cause you like ‘em. They have value to you. That’s what matters.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: How long are you staying?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Until we find your Rick.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: I found mine. I found mine.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Help!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Religious Morty
line: There is no escape, my son. We will find our peace in the next world.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: So what? Y-y-y-y-you’re just going to give up?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Religious Morty
line: We’re giving in to the power of the One True Morty. One day he will return!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: All religious Mortys
line: Praise the One True Morty!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Alright Mortys, listen up! My name is Morty Smith, from Earth dimension C-137! I know you’re scared, because I’m scared, but that’s no reason to accept our fate. We’re Mortys! We’re not defined by our relationships to Rick! Our destiny is our own!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty 1
line: This sounds like something the One True Morty might say. I’m sick of being a human shield! I-I-I-I wanna be a gardener!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty 2
line: I wanna write really crazy, intense action novels!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Hammer Morty
line: I’m more than just a hammer!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Religious Morty
line: He is the one true Morty! The one true Morty!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: All Mortys
line: Hooray!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Lobster alien
line: Hey, keep it down!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: All Mortys
line: Raaaaugh!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: You’ve lived quite a life, Rick. It’s a real shame you’re not gonna be around to see it through.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: You’re crying? Over a Morty?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: No, I’m just allergic to dipshits.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: Ugh, pathetic. We both know that if there’s any truth in the universe, it’s that Ricks don’t care about Mortys.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Evil Rick
line: Do your worst, you little bastards! Kill me! Do it! Do it!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Morty! Get me out of this! Come on!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: You’re lucky I’m not a Rick.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Point taken, but this is  no time for arcs.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: Yeah, hello?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Hey, what do me and O.J. not have in common?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: Huh? Wh-who is this?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: I found the real killer, biitch! Get over here!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: Yo ding-dong! We’re done here. Time to go.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Well Jerry, I  guess this means goodbye.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: W-w-well, does it have to? Heh, you, you look just like Rick. We could maybe… you know… get rid of him? I’m not saying kill him, necessarily, I-I’m also not saying necessarily not kill him, but-

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Jerry. W-we both know it wouldn’t work. It’s time to go back to our lives. I love you, Jerry. I love ya.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Wh-wh-what’s gonna happen to all these Mortys?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Council Rick 1
line: They’ll go back to their families, attend school regularly, play video games, date girls… poor little Rickless bastards.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Council Rick 1
line: Earth Rick C-137, the council apologises for its false accusation. And in the way of reparations for our terrible mistake, we would like to compensate you with this voucher for a free replacement Morty, in the event that  your current  Morty should-

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Uh, guys? Not a good time. Come on, Morty, let’s hit it.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Is it time for arcs yet, Rick? I did a pretty great job back there for a human cloaking device. Saved your ass.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Alright, Morty, don’t break an arm jerking yourself off.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Man, I can’t believe you, Rick! That right there! Tha-that was a great opportunity to show a little humanity. You know? To connect with me a little?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Hey Morty, you want connection? Go be part of some stupid club like all those dumb Ricks. You know, maybe I don’t connect because I’m the Rickest Rick there is. And you know, it would  go without saying that the Rickest Rick… would have the Mortyest Morty.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: It would go without saying, huh?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Yeah, it would. Did you hear me say it?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Nah…  The Mortyest Morty…

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Just don’t get too big for your loafers, Buster Brown. A cocky Morty could lead to some big problems. Could be a real bad thing for everybody.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Morty
line: Oh yeah, how’s that?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: I-I-I’ll explain when you’re older.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: What a mess…

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 2
line: Pride cometh before the fall. I guess he got what he deserved.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: What is that?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 2
line: Hand me the laser defibrillator.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Doofus Rick
line: Hey guys! Uh, c-can I help?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 2
line: No! Go clean the toilets! Maybe you’ll make friends with some turds!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: You make us ashamed to be ourselves!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 1
line: My god! I’ve seen this technology before! This Rick was being controlled remotely, puppeteered by somebody else. This is the receiver!

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick 2
line: Yeah, but where’s the transmitter?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Wubbalubbadubdub! Oh. Hey Jerry. Wh-wh-what are you doing in my room, buddy?

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Jerry
line: Nothing! I was just, um, checking the smoke detectors.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: Alright. Okay, get out.

episode name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind
name: Rick
line: What’s that dipshit doing out there? Are you friends with him? You know he eats his own shit, right? Oh my god, this is rich! I’ve got like  ten Ricks to call right now!

name: Man
line: Hey, golf is easy now!

name: Man
line: Aahh! Golf is hard again! Golf is hard agaaaaaaain!

name: Terry
line: The view here is the same as yours, Jim. A giant head has entered Earth’s gravity, triggering climate change and natural disasters we thought were impossible for at least another eight years.

name: Jim
line: Let’s not make this political, Terry. Do we know what this giant head wants?

name: Giant Head
line: SHOW ME WHAT YOU GOT.

name: Terry
line: Jim, you heard *static* said, “Show me what you got.”

name: Giant Head
line: SHOW ME WHAT YOU GOT. I WANT TO SEE WHAT YOU GOT.

name: Rick
line: Oh boy. Time to go, Morty.

name: Morty
line: Uhh, where?

name: Rick
line: The Pentagon. I mean, not THE Pentagon. *burp* The lame one, here on Earth.

name: Summer
line: Is it God? If it’s God, do we get out of school?

name: Beth
line: It’s not God, Summer.

name: Jerry
line: She’s allowed to think it’s God if she wants, honey!

name: Beth
line: Shut up, Jerry.

name: Jerry
line: Ok…

name: Beth
line: Dad, what do you know about this?

name: Rick
line: Morty and I are going to look into it. You guys hold tight.

name: Mr. Goldenfold
line: Scary stuff, huh? Pretty freaky. Hi, I’m Morty’s math teacher. I’m also part of the street team inviting folks to the church downtown so we can pray together.

name: Beth
line: How is praying going to help?

name: Mr. Goldenfold
line: Ma’am, a giant head in the sky is controlling the weather. Did you wanna play checkers? Let’s be rational! I’ll see you at God’s house!

name: President
line: Gentlemen, gentlemen, one at a time! Simon?

name: Simon
line: SETI, NORAD, and every broadcaster on the planet are attempting to show this being what humanity’s got. String theory, world history, the human genome.

name: Nathan
line: Have you tried sending it launch codes? Mr. President, what America’s got is 70,000 megatons of KABOOM-BOOM! And I say we show it right up this floating head’s ass!

name: Guards
line: Hold it! Don’t move!

name: Rick
line: Stay back! This watch turns people into snakes!

name: President
line: Stand down. Everybody stand down! I’m the leader of these people and I’m unarmed. There’s no need for any more snake-makery.

name: Rick
line: My name is Rick Sanchez. This here’s my grandson Morty.

name: Everyone
line: Hi, Morty.

name: Morty
line: Hey.

name: Rick
line: I’ve seen enough of the galaxy to know that what we’ve got here is a Cromulon from the Cygnus-5 Expanse. So you can forget about nukes, and you can forget about math.  This head won’t go away until *burp* Earth shows them it’s got a hit song.

name: Everyone
line: Seriously, that’s impossible, etc…

name: Simon
line: You mean like Vivaldi?

name: Rick
line: No, Frasier. A live performance of a newly-written, catchy, original song. The Cromulon feed on the talent and showmanship of less-evolved lifeforms.

name: President
line: All right, all right. Thank you, Mr. Sanchez. Change of plan, people. Get me Pharrell, Randy Newman, Billy Corgan, and The-Dream.  The-Dream? He wrote “Umbrella” and “Single Ladies”? You people haven’t heard of The-Dream?

name: Rick
line: You’re gonna wanna put them on that giant speaker system at your sonic testing facility at Area 51.

name: Nathan
line: How do you know about that?

name: President
line: For God’s sake, Nathan, the man turns people into snakes. He can use Google Maps.

name: Aide
line: Sir! Pharrell, Newman, Corgan, and that Dream guy. They’re all dead.

name: President
line: What? How is that possible? Do people just die when I name them?

name: Aide
line: The Grammys, sir. There was an earthquake and all the musicians...  All the famous ones, they’re gone.

name: President
line: Dear God.

name: Aide
line: Hold on, sir, just a minute. Ice-T survived. He’s inbound on an F-15, ETA two hours.

name: Rick
line: Good luck, Mr. President.

name: Simon
line: Sir, the magnetic poles are about to reverse. In two hours, there may not be an Earth to save.

name: President
line: Sanchez! Are you a musician?

name: Rick
line: I dabble, Mr. President.

name: President
line: Get this man and his grandson on a Blackhawk to Area 51.

name: Father Bob
line: People! Everyone! Remain calm! Every crisis of faith is an opportunity for more faith! When God deals you an 11, you don’t fold! You double down, and always hit on a soft 16. That means you, Jews.

name: Jew
line: I beg your pardon, pastor, but the last I looked outside, it seems to be you that’s been dealt the weak hand. Jews rule!  Nobody? Ok, tough church.

name: Principal Vagina
line: Hi, Principal Vagina. The name’s real, possibly Scandinavian. I’m just gonna come out and make this pitch. The old gods are dead. Fuck all previous existing religions. All hail the one true god, the giant head in the sky.

name: Principal Vagina
line: Ah, di di di di.  Bob, Bob, I get it. But unless this  can beat that… what have you done for me lately?  So if you wanna excuse me, I’m going out on the sidewalk and dropping to my knees and pledging my eternal soul to the thing that literally controls the fucking weather!  Outta my way!

name: Pastor Bob
line: Ok, if sanity’s been restored to this assembly, I’d like to talk about the cost of repairing our new organ. Sally, the plate, please.

name: Mr. Goldenfold
line: Ohhhh, this is my favorite part!

name: Morty
line: Rick, are you really a musician?

name: Rick
line: Who’s NOT a musician, Morty?

name: Morty
line: Me!

name: Rick
line: Yeah, not with that attitude.

name: Jump Master
line: We’re in the drop zone! I’m the jump master! My name’s Jamey! With an E-Y! Go, go, go!

name: Morty
line: B-b-but we don’t have a song!

name: Principal Vagina
line: Giant head in the sky, please forgive all that we’ve done. We’re sorry for increased levels of emissions and our racism. And of course, the amber alerts I keep ignoring on my phone.

name: Rick and Morty
line: WhooooOOOOAHHHH!!!!

name: Rick
line: All right, Morty, let’s get ready to do it! Why don’t you, uh, find a button on one of those keyboards and lay down some kind of beat?

name: Morty
line: Rick, I think we need to cut our losses. We get our family and portal out of here!

name: Rick
line: Morty! Good music comes from people who are relaxed. Just hit a button, Morty! Gimme a beat!

name: Morty
line: Oh man, ok, all right, um…

name: Rick
line: Ahhhhh yeahhhhh

name: Nathan
line: Get… schwifty? What the hell is that?

name: President
line: It’s our world’s best effort, that’s what.

name: Rick
line: Take off your pants and your panties

name: Nathan
line: Mr. Bulldops?

name: President
line: Don’t analyze it, Nathan. It’s working!

name: Rick
line: Take a shit on the floor

name: Pastor Bob
line: And third-level donors get our all access family pass.

name: Summer
line: Listen! The storm is stopping!

name: Rick
line: Hey, take your pants off

name: Giant Head
line: Hmmmm.

name: Principal Vagina
line: Please be kind to us for we are but tiny things with entire bodies stuck to your ground.

name: Giant Head
line: I LIKE WHAT YOU GOT. GOOD JOB.

name: Beth
line: Now hold on a second, let’s be rational about this.

name: Beth
line: No, I’m… I’m just saying, we don’t know if there’s a cause-effect relationship --

name: Beth
line: Oh, God, what’s going on now?

name: President
line: What the hell happened?

name: Aide
line: Mr. President, you’re gonna wanna see this.

name: Rick
line: I think planet Earth has just been transported.

name: Principal Vagina
line: The head has left and sent its children!

name: Beth
line: Holy CRAP!

name: Summer
line: Oh dear giant head, we apologize for that discussion! It will never happen again!

name: Simon
line: Sir, we’ve started picking up on a garbled signal. We’re decrypting it now.

name: Cromulon
line: WE ASKED THEM TO SHOW US WHAT THEY GOT. AND THEY DID. NOW WE’LL SEE WHICH OF THEM HAS GOT THE MOST. 24 HOURS, FIVE PLANETS, FIVE SONGS. BUT IN THE END, THERE CAN ONLY BE ONE. PLANET MUSIC! All participation is involuntary. Disqualified and losing planets are disintegrated by plasma ray.

name: Rick
line: Uhh, it’s probably a bad time to mention it, but any astronauts you guys had in orbit are definitely dead.

name: Cromulon
line: Welcome back to Planet Music! First up, let’s hear the latest song from planet Parblesnops. The Greebybobes! SHOW ME WHAT YOU GOT.

name: Greebybobe
line: Hold it, hold it, stop! Music isn’t about competition or captivity! If you love music, you love freedom. Let these worlds be free, please!

name: Cromulon
line: DISQUALIFIED!

name: Cromulon
line: There’s one every season. Moving on to planet Arbolez Meterosos. Arbolian Meterososians. SHOW US WHAT YOU GOT.

name: Arbolian Meterososian
line: Ah two, three, four…

name: Aide
line: Rick, Morty, Ice-T. The timetable’s moved up. Earth’s on in six hours.

name: Morty
line: Like we’re not already under enough pressure!

name: Rick and Ice-T
line: Whoa ho ho ho ho!

name: Rick
line: Geez, Morty. The guy’s just doing his job. Take it easy.

name: Morty
line: Rick, Ice-T, could you guys take it less easy?! We’ve got six hours to come up with a song!

name: Rick
line: Genius happens in the moment, Morty.

name: Morty
line: Well, can we at least go get our family? You know, so we can take them with-with-with us if we lose?

name: Rick
line: That’s planning for failure, Morty. Even dumber than regular planning.  Balls.

name: Rick
line: Morty, Morty, stop! Listen! There’s only so much charge left in this thing. If we portal home from here and back, we’re not gonna have enough charge left to get off-world. Get it?

name: Morty
line: What?!

name: Rick
line: Yeah, *burp* you see, I try to shelter you from certain realities, *burp* Morty. Cause if I let you make me nervous, then we can’t get schwifty.

name: Morty
line: Stop saying it like it’s a thing! You made it up!

name: Rick
line: Hey, Morty! Could you lick my…

name: Morty
line: Rick, cut it out! That’s not funny, Rick!

name: Nathan
line: I’ve seen enough. These guys are one-hit wonders.

name: President
line: And what’s your plan, General?

name: Nathan
line: We still have the nuclear option. On my word, we can launch a nuclear missile at every one of those heads in the sky.

name: President
line: Our planet’s held captive on a live game show and your solution is to shoot the audience? You can put your faith in nukes if we get through this, General. Until then, I’ll put mine in Rick and Morty. “Get Schwifty” was a jam.

name: Principal Vagina
line: Hello? Yes sir, yeah. Thank you sir, thank you. He says he’s proud of what we’re doing and hopes we have a great Ascension Festival! Happy Ascension!

name: All
line: Happy Ascension!

name: Beth
line: We should pack up and leave town now.

name: Jerry
line: I think it’s inspiring that our community is coping with fear in a way that involves a festival and homemade ice cream. If you’d stop being such an evangelical atheist, you might start enjoying yourself.

name: Jerry
line: Whoa! Look at you! You’re wearing the hat and everything!

name: Summer
line: Here’s yours!  Mom, do you mind if I cook dinner tonight?

name: Beth
line: Yeah, sure. Wait, what??

name: Summer
line: I love you guys. You gave me life. And it’s the will of the many heads that all children honor their parents.

name: Beth
line: Dinner sounds nice.

name: Ethan
line: Pardon, Mr. and Mrs. Smith. Summer, are you coming to the Ascension?

name: Summer
line: Father, can we please go to the Ascension?

name: Jerry
line: Sure! Let’s go to the Ascension. Wh-wh-what is it?

name: Principal Vagina
line: We hereby send these un-wantables skyward that they might be inhaled by the many heads, later to be sneezed back to us as better babies!  Headward, free now to rise.  Headward, free now to rise.  Headward, free now to rise.

name: Summer
line: Oh yes, yes! Rise to the giant head! You are free to be free!

name: Ice-T
line: A squeegee comes up from the garage, right? And he’s got a lobster in one hand and movie tickets in the other. He’s like, “I’m ready!”

name: Ice-T
line: Who would take a lobster to see Iron Man 3?

name: Ice-T
line: Aw, damn. We’re out of original flavor Fig Newtons. I should get going anyway.

name: Rick
line: Wait, wait, wait! Come on, h-hold on a second!

name: Morty
line: What?!

name: Ice-T
line: Damn. You didn’t tell me you fuck around with portals and shit.

name: Morty
line: That’s it!

name: Rick
line: Whoa, whoa! Morty! Give me that!

name: Morty
line: You lied! You lied about the charge! You were just being lazy! Get back! Sit down!

name: Rick
line: Morty, just put it down. You don’t know what you’re doing.

name: Morty
line: I’m going to go find Mom and Dad.

name: Rick
line: Nooooo!

name: Rick
line: Ahhhh, shit!

name: President
line: Ah, shit.

name: Morty
line: Ahhh, shit.

name: Summer
line: And then Ethan played guitar and we learned the Seven Contemplations of the Head by singing them. It was really fun. Praise be the head!

name: Jerry and Beth
line: Praise be the…

name: Jerry
line: Yeah.

name: Principal Vagina
line: Hi folks, Head Priest Vagina. Thanks for farming all those potatoes. It’s 6 p.m., so if you’re a parent, you’re now entitled to adoration from your children.

name: Summer
line: I’m going to start dinner!

name: Beth
line: I don’t know what to say. Summer is doing really well here.

name: Jerry
line: She’s aced every test in potato class, and look how important potatoes have become.

name: Beth
line: She’s not getting pregnant or doing drugs or missing curfew…

name: Balloon Man
line: Please help me! You can reach me if you try. Please help me!!

name: Beth
line: That’s not our business as long as Summer is thriving!

name: Summer
line: Taco time!  I hope it pleases you as the head desires.

name: Beth
line: That’s wonderful, Summer!

name: Jerry
line: We’re so proud of you. But honestly, you don’t have to make dinner every night.

name: Summer
line: Of course I do, silly!  Oh my God, daddy, I’m sorry I called you silly! I’m so sorry!  Heavenly head and cranial creator! Forgive my transgressions against family and community! May my chores complete me as I complete them!

name: Birdperson
line: Morty.

name: Morty
line: Birdperson?

name: Birdperson
line: You appear to be dying. I will make efforts to prevent this, but can promise nothing.

name: Rick
line: Wh-What do you think, Ice? Probably a little over-developed.

name: Ice-T
line: Shit. Over-developed, under-developed. Bad songs are bad songs.

name: Rick
line: Well, do you think maybe, could you give me some help with it, or… ?

name: Ice-T
line: Ah, hell no, man. You do your thing, but I can’t afford to get my pride wrapped up in your shame. You know what I’m sayin’?

name: Rick
line: Ice, I don’t want to be a negative Nelly or anything, but *burp* if Morty doesn’t come back with my portal gun and I eat it out there, it’s, uh, kind of your problem too.

name: Ice-T
line: Pfff. I ain’t worried about no Earth blowin’ up, man.

name: Rick
line: What? Why not?

name: Ice-T
line: Yo, this is why.

name: Rick
line: What the fuck? You can turn into ice?

name: Ice-T
line: My story begins at the dawn of time in the far away realm of Alphabetrium. There, every being is a letter of the alphabet. But I was frozen and exiled to the cosmos by my elders as punishment for not caring enough about anything. Earth is just one of the many stops on my lifelong journey with no destination. So you better believe I don’t care if it blows up! Cause I’ll just be ice, floatin’ through space, like a comet!

name: Rick
line: Take it from me, Ice. *burp* You can’t just *burp* float around space not caring about stuff forever.

name: Ice-T
line: Pshhhh. Man, watch me. Good luck, Rick.

name: President
line: Ok, things are getting out of hand. I better make sure Rick has everything he needs to “get schwifty.”

name: Nathan
line: Oh, for God’s sake, that’s enough.

name: President
line: What the hell are you doing, Nathan? I’m the goddamn President of the United fuckin’ States!

name: Nathan
line: I’m setting the nuclear option to launch one minute into Earth’s performance. And you, Mr. President, I hope you like being hit in the face with a gun!

name: President
line: Wait, wait, wait, why-why --

name: Birdperson
line: I believe I can access the history of Rick’s gun and help you get back to him.

name: Morty
line: But can you help me get to my family? You know, at my house?

name: Birdperson
line: Is your intention to abandon Rick using his own portal gun? In bird culture, this is considered a dick move.

name: Morty
line: All of Rick’s moves are dick moves! Wh-what am I eating? What is this, bird seed?

name: Birdperson
line: It is random debris. I found it in my carpet. I don’t know what humans eat.

name: Tammy
line: You know what THIS human eats!

name: Birdperson
line: Don’t be gross, Tammy.

name: Tammy
line: Bird… dick.

name: Morty
line: Tammy… gross. Birdperson, you always stick up for Rick, but he doesn’t care about anyone but himself. He doesn’t think about the consequences of anything he does.

name: Birdperson
line: And as a result, he has the power to save or destroy entire worlds. And he is the reason you and I know each other. And the reason I’m alive at all.

name: Morty
line: What’s that? Who’s that baby?

name: Birdperson
line: Morty, suppose you could retrieve your family from Earth but had to abandon Rick. I could give your loved ones shelter on Birdworld, even jobs, possibly as worm ranchers. How often do you think you might look up at the stars and wonder what might have been had you just put your faith in Rick?

name: Cromulon
line: That was Chunky Tunk with “Full Ming Mong, Empty Gorp Dorp.” Up next, planet Earth!

name: Morty
line: Oh God! We’re up?!?!

name: Principal Vagina
line: Jerry and Beth, your family is a golden example of what Headism has to offer the world.

name: Beth
line: The world?

name: Principal Vagina
line: Headism is a hit. We’re taking it worldwide and would like Jerry to be our church’s “Head” of Advertising.

name: Jerry
line: You… would?

name: Principal Vagina
line: Beth, we’d like to promote you from horse surgeon, straight past human surgeon, to “Head” of Medicine.

name: Beth
line: That’s my dream! That’s my dream.

name: Jerry
line: Thank you. This is all so overwhelming, but, uh… we can’t.

name: Beth
line: Absolutely not.

name: Principal Vagina
line: I’m sorry?

name: Beth
line: We’ve been waiting 16 years for our daughter to respect us, but the key is, it has to be “our” daughter, not this person she’s become.

name: Jerry
line: We’ll take our chances raising her without fancy new jobs outside of a potato-based religion.  And you know what? I’m sick of pretending that we’re together because of the kids in the first place! I married you because you’re the love of my life!

name: Beth
line: And I‘m lucky to have you and I never tell you that! You know, we will come out of this stronger as a family!

name: Beth
line: Please don’t do this, please don’t do this! Summer!

name: Jerry
line: Summer, listen carefully. I stole a paper clip and I have it in my cheek but I don’t know what to do with it and it hurts.

name: Summer
line: You’re going to be ok!  You will come back as babies!

name: Jerry
line: I AM a baby! I’m a baby NOW!

name: Morty
line: Hello? Is anybody here?  Mr. President!

name: President
line: This is Bluebird. Code tango-niner-alpha. Abort launch. Abort! Hello?  He’s blocked me out.

name: Morty
line: Sir, I need to get to the stage and help Rick get schwifty!

name: President
line: It won’t matter how schwifty you get, Morty. The General’s got nukes set to launch halfway through Earth’s song!

name: Morty
line: Oh my God! C-c-can you fly a Blackhawk?

name: President
line: Can the Pope’s dick fit through a donut?

name: Morty
line: Uhhh, I’m not sure?

name: President
line: Exactly!

name: Cromulon
line: SHOW ME WHAT YOU GOT.

name: Rick
line: Ahem.  Uhhh… lop-oo-lop-oo-lop-oo-dups, nop-oo-nop-oo-nop-oo-nuts.

name: Principal Vagina
line: Headward free now to rise!

name: Mr. Goldenfold
line: Hey! Look at the heads! Looks like the heads are gettin’ angry!

name: President
line: I’m really bad at this, Morty! There are way too many buttons on this thing!

name: Morty
line: Mr. President, if I’ve learned one thing today, it’s that sometimes, you have to not give a fuck!

name: Rick
line: Nup-oo-nup-oo-nup-oo-nups… ooh, tough crowd.

name: Principal Vagina
line: I’m sure that has… that has nothing to do with this.

name: Summer
line: The heads are displeased!

name: Ethan
line: Summer!

name: Rick
line: Morty!

name: Mr. Goldenfold
line: The heads love this! They love it when we DON’T kill the Smith family!

name: Principal Vagina
line: No! Stop that! You’re not allowed to interpret the will of the heads!

name: President
line: Call off the nuclear strike! This is the President. Stop the nuclear missile launch!

name: Nathan
line: Just launch the missiles!

name: Cromulon
line: BOO! NOT COOL!

name: Principal Vagina
line: I’m the only one that speaks to the heads!

name: Cromulon
line: DISQUALIFIED!

name: Mr. Goldenfold
line: The heads disqualified Vagina! Get him!

name: Cromulon
line: DISQUALIFIED! DISQUALIFIED!

name: All
line: Ice-T?

name: Ice-T
line: That’s right, it’s me, Ice-T! I care now! You made me care more! With all due respect, I’d like to hear what Rick and Morty have to play.

name: Morty
line: What do you say, Rick?

name: Rick
line: I say…  Let’s do it!

name: Rick
line: All right!

name: Morty
line: Ohhhh yeahhhh!

name: Rick
line: Come on, here we go!

name: Morty
line: Ohhhh yeahhhh!

name: Rick
line: Say it with me!

name: All
line: Head bent over

name: Principal Vagina
line: Ohhh my GOOOOODDDD!!!

name: All
line: Head bent over

name: Cromulon
line: After 988 seasons of Planet Music, the Cromulons have decided to declare Earth the final winner and bring our musical reality show to a conclusion. Goodbye!

name: All
line: Yeah, we did it!

name: Mr. Goldenfold
line: Did he just say “musical reality show”?

name: Jerry
line: Yeah, it’s possible that we may have been correlating some things that weren’t actually related at all.

name: Principal Vagina
line: HEEEEELLLLPPPP!!!!!

name: Beth
line: We should go get him.

name: President
line: I hope I can call on you again if we need you, Morty.

name: Morty
line: Sure thing! And I was kinda hoping that I could get a selfie with you?

name: President
line: Actually, if you try to tell anyone what happened here, we’ll deny it and probably worse.

name: Morty
line: Understood.

name: Nathan
line: DIIIIEEEE!!!!

name: President
line: Why didn’t he turn into a snake?

name: Rick
line: Trade secret, Mr. President. Particle beam in a wristwatch… snake holster on the leg.

name: President
line: I love this man!

name: Ice-T
line: Magnesium-J, Hydrogen-F. Father.

name: Magnesium-J
line: Word of your selfless acts on the Earth planet have travelled across the galaxy.

name: Ice-T
line: I have changed. I am ready to rejoin my brethren on Alphabetrium.

name: Magnesium-J
line: Very well. Your exile ends today!

name: Magnesium-J
line: Welcome home... Water-T.

name: Purple-P
line: The Numbericons! They’re attacking!

name: Magnesium-J
line: Battle stations!

name: Water-T
line: Father!

name: Magma-Q
line: I love you son. I should have never turned you to ice.

name: Magnesium-J
line: Water-T, where are you going? There’s too many of them!

name: Water-T
line: Then I better crunch the numbers.
